Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.43,0:00:07.81,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,And in the clover's fifth leaf resides...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.81,0:00:09.31,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,a devil.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.07,0:00:12.36,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,What Asta, who was born without magic,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.36,0:00:14.71,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,gained from the five-leaf grimoire was
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.71,0:00:18.72,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,the power of anti-magic, \Nwhich nullifies any magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.00,0:00:23.93,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Meanwhile, the Dark Triad \Nof the Spade Kingdom
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.93,0:00:26.80,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,also possessed the powers of \Nthe devils from the underworld,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.80,0:00:29.72,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,and began invading the other kingdoms.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.65,0:00:33.75,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Asta continued to fight \Nwhile believing in himself,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.25,0:00:38.30,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,along with his friends... \Nto protect this world!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.92,0:00:50.52,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,After a fierce battle, \NYami and Asta defeated Dante.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.05,0:00:52.86,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,We win!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.86,0:00:58.22,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,But then Zenon attacked, and Yami was \Ntaken away along with Vangeance.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.78,0:01:02.36,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Yami!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.89,0:01:10.04,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,That night, Asta tried to escape the \Ninfirmary tower in order to rescue Yami,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.04,0:01:12.05,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,and he ran into...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.21,0:01:16.51,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,The Vice Captain of the Black Bulls, Nacht.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.47,0:01:22.68,flashback,Nacht,0000,0000,0000,,If you so desire, I'll show you \Nhow to use the devil's powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.65,0:01:28.34,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Asta arrived with Nacht to an emergency \NMagic Knight Squad Captains' meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.65,0:01:30.98,main,Nozel,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.25,0:01:35.49,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,He's a vice captain... with the Black Bulls.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.77,0:01:38.93,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,He's been acting as a spy \Nin the Spade Kingdom,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.93,0:01:41.74,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,though I didn't know that \Nhe was devil-possessed.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.79,0:01:46.85,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Back in the Spade Kingdom, the ritual \Nof the advent of Qliphoth was underway.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.85,0:01:50.92,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Once the ritual was complete, this world \Nwould be connected with the underworld,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.16,0:01:55.80,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,and Yami and Vangeance would \Nlose their lives as sacrifices.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.59,0:02:01.35,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,In three days, the first of seven gates\N to the underworld will open.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.35,0:02:04.01,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,They must fight the Dark Triad\N before that can happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.01,0:02:07.87,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,Then we should also ask the \NHeart Kingdom for help.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.87,0:02:10.60,main,Marx,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I haven't been able to \Nget a hold of them since yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.18,0:02:13.36,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Meanwhile, it looked as if
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.36,0:02:16.76,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Vanica had destroyed the Heart \NKingdom with her magic, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.17,0:02:27.49,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.93,0:03:54.21,Ep Title,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\t(1,1134,\c&H0900AD&)}The Devil-Binding Ritual
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.41,0:04:05.56,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.30,0:04:09.11,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,The leader of the Eye of the Midnight Sun,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.11,0:04:11.35,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,and the elves from the Third Eye...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.10,0:04:16.04,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.84,0:04:19.84,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Where are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.06,0:04:36.58,main,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,This is Elysia.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.09,0:04:41.59,main,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,It's a secluded area in a strong magic region \Nlocated deep within the Heart Kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.92,0:04:45.64,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,This place is overflowing with \Nincredibly dense mana.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.21,0:04:51.04,main,Elf boy,0000,0000,0000,,So they're awake.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.94,0:04:53.17,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Who are these children?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.69,0:04:59.33,main,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,They are the descendants of \NPrincess Tetia of the Clover Kingdom and Licht.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.31,0:05:01.28,main,Noelle and Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.63,0:05:05.03,italics,Nero,0000,0000,0000,,Back then...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.71,0:05:18.84,flashback,Nero,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Tetia...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.49,0:05:22.47,flashback,Nero,0000,0000,0000,,She's still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.88,0:05:29.89,flashback,Nero,0000,0000,0000,,This mana... One of the twins she \Nwas carrying has also survived!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.37,0:05:37.97,italics,Nero,0000,0000,0000,,I immediately sealed Lady Tetia's wounds
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.79,0:05:40.85,italics,Nero,0000,0000,0000,,and rushed to Prince Lumiere's side.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.21,0:05:45.40,italics,Nero,0000,0000,0000,,After that...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.77,0:06:04.27,italics,Nero,0000,0000,0000,,When I woke up in the form of a bird,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.27,0:06:06.43,italics,Nero,0000,0000,0000,,many years had passed,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.43,0:06:09.06,italics,Nero,0000,0000,0000,,and I had no idea what became of Lady Tetia.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.33,0:06:13.80,italics,Nero,0000,0000,0000,,But she survived.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.87,0:06:20.19,italics,Nero,0000,0000,0000,,Her life was saved!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.25,0:06:23.94,italics,Nero,0000,0000,0000,,Children born of an elf and a human...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.55,0:06:29.57,italics,Nero,0000,0000,0000,,Prince Lumiere... \NThe lives you had hoped for...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.13,0:06:33.45,italics,Nero,0000,0000,0000,,The new world you wished for...\N is right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.94,0:06:39.37,main,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,This is the new village of the elves.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.95,0:06:42.41,main,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,Once we found out about this place,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.25,0:06:47.95,main,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,I felt as though I understood why \Nwe stayed behind in this era.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.09,0:06:55.47,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you save us?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.00,0:06:59.02,main,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,Because Dryad, the guardian deity of Elysia,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.02,0:07:02.23,main,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,sent a divine revelation telling us to save you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.96,0:07:04.24,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Dryad?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.22,0:07:11.60,main,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,After receiving the divine revelation, \Nwe rushed to the Heart Kingdom,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.60,0:07:12.91,main,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,but we didn't make it in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.74,0:07:20.46,main,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.12,0:07:30.30,main,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,All of you had somehow used your own \Npowers to survive those explosions.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.68,0:08:17.64,main,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to you, the citizens of \Nthe Heart Kingdom were safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.14,0:08:23.58,main,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,It's amazing that you weren't annihilated \Nwhen faced with such powerful enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.09,0:08:26.73,main,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,You must've gotten even stronger \Nover these past few months.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.99,0:08:32.06,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,That's not enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.98,0:08:36.06,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't protect them. \NI couldn't defeat them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.63,0:08:39.33,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Even though we'd trained for \Nmonths and gotten stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.49,0:08:44.83,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Now that Loropechika's been kidnapped, \Nthere's no guarantee she'll remain safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.92,0:08:46.79,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,We have to...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.48,0:08:51.76,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,We have to get stronger right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.76,0:08:52.71,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.71,0:08:55.88,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,You're all stronger than we are, aren't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.88,0:08:58.26,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me how you got so strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.00,0:09:04.12,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,Wow... Is that really how you ask \Nsomeone for a favor, Little Miss Royalty?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.40,0:09:08.09,main,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,Do you truly believe you can \Ndefeat an enemy that you
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.09,0:09:10.36,main,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,couldn't defeat after months of training
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.36,0:09:12.28,main,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,just by training a little more?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.49,0:09:18.03,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I know it won't be that easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.30,0:09:20.03,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.94,0:09:23.58,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,It's even harder to give \Nup on becoming stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.85,0:09:27.38,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Right, you guys?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.79,0:09:28.79,main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.10,0:09:31.29,main,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.29,0:09:34.13,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez! I see you're all \Nstill a pain in the ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.77,0:09:37.43,main,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,Then you will be able to become stronger
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.85,0:09:40.61,main,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,by using the elves' esoteric art,\Nultimate magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.10,0:09:45.85,main,Rill,0000,0000,0000,,I'm worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.57,0:09:50.02,main,Rill,0000,0000,0000,,I hope Charmy and the others are okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.99,0:10:02.20,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Gaja!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.74,0:10:09.77,italics,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,I see... So that's what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.49,0:10:15.76,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to attack the Spade Kingdom \Nthree days from now, early in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.76,0:10:17.13,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,What will you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.38,0:10:19.45,main,Gaja,0000,0000,0000,,We shall fight with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.45,0:10:21.72,main,Gaja,0000,0000,0000,,All of the Spirit Guardians are safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.89,0:10:26.76,main,Gaja,0000,0000,0000,,On the honor of the Heart Kingdom,\Nwe will reclaim our queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.28,0:10:31.40,italics,Gaja,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Noelle and the others are also \Ngetting ready to reenter the battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.40,0:10:33.65,italics,Gaja,0000,0000,0000,,But it will be up to them if \Nthey can make it in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.97,0:10:37.28,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Thank you for contacting us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.92,0:10:52.20,main,Gaja,0000,0000,0000,,I will save you, no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.76,0:10:56.40,italics,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,I will not let him die.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.72,0:10:59.88,italics,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,Wait for me, Yami!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.61,0:11:03.60,main,Rill,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness Charmy, \Nthe other Magic Knights,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.60,0:11:05.82,main,Rill,0000,0000,0000,,and the Spirit Guardians seem to be safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.82,0:11:07.57,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I guess Noelle and the others are training!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.57,0:11:09.65,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I want to train as soon as possible, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.65,0:11:10.89,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Vice Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.34,0:11:12.94,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,H-Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.06,0:11:15.61,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Vice Captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.47,0:11:38.89,main,Nacht,0000,0000,0000,,In three days, we will gather \Nthe Magic Knights' elite
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.89,0:11:41.72,main,Nacht,0000,0000,0000,,and attack the Spade Kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.96,0:11:48.20,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,You're... the Vice Captain \Nof the Black Bulls?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.64,0:11:49.82,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you here now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.38,0:11:52.77,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Why have you never shown up even once before?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.56,0:11:56.44,main,Nacht,0000,0000,0000,,Because I hate the Black Bulls.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.55,0:12:01.56,main,Nacht,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do whatever it takes as long as \NI get to operate as a Magic Knight.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.06,0:12:05.86,main,Nacht,0000,0000,0000,,It's honestly quite convenient being \Na vice captain. I can do what I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.82,0:12:09.67,main,Nacht,0000,0000,0000,,I despise people who \Ncan't do things properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.67,0:12:13.52,main,Nacht,0000,0000,0000,,The Black Bulls are known as "the squad \Nof good-for-nothings with more damage
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.52,0:12:15.14,main,Nacht,0000,0000,0000,,than exploits to their name," right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.53,0:12:20.14,main,Nacht,0000,0000,0000,,It sounds like you were involved \Nin the battle six months ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.14,0:12:23.96,main,Nacht,0000,0000,0000,,but that doesn't exactly erase \Nall of your past failures.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.67,0:12:28.10,main,Nacht,0000,0000,0000,,The vulgar witch who drinks all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.95,0:12:33.31,main,Nacht,0000,0000,0000,,The spatial mage who's so careless with \Nwomen that it interfered with his missions.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.02,0:12:36.52,main,Nacht,0000,0000,0000,,The former convict who's a ruined noble.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.84,0:12:40.03,main,Nacht,0000,0000,0000,,There's also... Though I don't \Nsee them here right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.87,0:12:44.10,main,Nacht,0000,0000,0000,,the obviously evil-looking \Ndelinquent peasant,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.10,0:12:47.26,main,Nacht,0000,0000,0000,,and the obviously evil-looking, \Nbelligerent, mask-wearing peasant.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.26,0:12:48.53,main,Nacht,0000,0000,0000,,Et cetera, et cetera.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.22,0:12:53.21,main,Nacht,0000,0000,0000,,Though it's clear that \Ngood-for-nothing assembled you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.63,0:12:58.39,main,Grey,0000,0000,0000,,Th-They're all good people!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.39,0:13:01.09,main,Grey,0000,0000,0000,,P-Please don't just judge \Nthem by how they look!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.09,0:13:05.63,main,Nacht,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if you don't want to be judged \Nby how you look, don't look like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.30,0:13:10.01,main,Nacht,0000,0000,0000,,When evil-looking people
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.01,0:13:13.61,main,Nacht,0000,0000,0000,,or those who have committed evil deeds \Nin the past suddenly do something good,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.61,0:13:15.02,main,Nacht,0000,0000,0000,,that twist makes them more likable.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.59,0:13:19.11,main,Nacht,0000,0000,0000,,And I absolutely hate that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.17,0:13:24.76,main,Nacht,0000,0000,0000,,The greatest people are those \Nwho are good from the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.76,0:13:29.71,main,Nacht,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, you're nothing more than \Ngood-for-nothings that Yami gathered.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.56,0:13:34.89,main,Nacht,0000,0000,0000,,If you still want to save \Nthat worthless man's life...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.57,0:13:38.88,main,Nacht,0000,0000,0000,,Get stronger in the next two days.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.21,0:13:53.89,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I've been wondering. What is this magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.47,0:13:55.81,main,Nacht,0000,0000,0000,,It's shadow magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.81,0:13:59.81,main,Nacht,0000,0000,0000,,I, and whatever I'm touching, \Ncan move from one shadow to another.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.55,0:14:03.11,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,So it's like spatial magic. \NThat's super convenient!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.11,0:14:04.10,main,Nacht,0000,0000,0000,,We're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.26,0:14:07.46,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What's this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.07,0:14:15.54,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Whose house is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.74,0:14:20.55,main,Nacht,0000,0000,0000,,This house belongs to a certain noble.\N A former noble, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.25,0:14:23.46,main,Nacht,0000,0000,0000,,We're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.59,0:14:27.47,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Here? But there isn't anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.70,0:14:32.02,main,Nacht,0000,0000,0000,,Shadow Magic: Dark Garden Invitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.24,0:14:47.69,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Now where are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.61,0:15:04.04,main,Nacht,0000,0000,0000,,For the next two days, I'll teach you all \NI know about using the magic of devils.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.77,0:15:08.05,main,Nacht,0000,0000,0000,,And as a result, you'll grow exponentially.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.97,0:15:12.06,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,So we're training, then? Heck yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.50,0:15:16.79,main,Nacht,0000,0000,0000,,Currently, you aren't using the \Ndevil's powers to the fullest extent.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.22,0:15:21.08,main,Nacht,0000,0000,0000,,You're just using the power \Nthat trickles down from the devil.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.04,0:15:26.94,main,Nacht,0000,0000,0000,,We are about to perform \Na devil-binding ritual.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.94,0:15:30.45,main,Nacht,0000,0000,0000,,You'll make a contract with a devil \Nand formally make its power your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.45,0:15:33.57,main,Nacht,0000,0000,0000,,It's a forbidden ceremony that puts \Na devil's powers at your command.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.46,0:15:35.83,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,A devil-binding ritual...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.35,0:15:39.83,main,Nacht,0000,0000,0000,,This ritual will allow you to \Ndraw out the devil's powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.35,0:15:43.32,main,Nacht,0000,0000,0000,,This ritual requires a connection to a devil.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.09,0:15:48.29,main,Nacht,0000,0000,0000,,Usually, you'd use a relic connected \Nto the devil, like I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.29,0:15:52.84,main,Nacht,0000,0000,0000,,This will temporarily allow you \Nto summon the devil to our world.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.63,0:15:55.55,main,Nacht,0000,0000,0000,,But you're a different story.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.11,0:15:58.52,main,Nacht,0000,0000,0000,,Your arm, your grimoire...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.95,0:16:03.07,main,Nacht,0000,0000,0000,,Your existence itself has a \Ndeep connection to the devil.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.56,0:16:07.32,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Got it! So what do I have to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.37,0:16:11.32,main,Nacht,0000,0000,0000,,Summon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.92,0:16:17.33,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.75,0:16:24.95,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,The devil...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.16,0:16:28.26,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,My right arm!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.65,0:16:34.84,main,Liebe,0000,0000,0000,,To think you'd let me out yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.32,0:16:40.10,main,Nacht,0000,0000,0000,,Fight the devil... and win.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.56,0:16:44.32,main,Nacht,0000,0000,0000,,Use your powers to make \Nthe devil submit to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.73,0:16:47.57,main,Nacht,0000,0000,0000,,That's the moment the devil's \Npowers will become yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.14,0:16:53.36,main,Liebe,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while since I've \Ncome to the physical world.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.66,0:16:58.87,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Devil... Is that your true form?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.02,0:17:06.37,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,There's something I've been \Nmeaning to tell you forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.03,0:17:10.12,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.87,0:17:14.13,main,Liebe,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.57,0:17:19.30,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Your powers helped me out \Ntime after time in battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.41,0:17:40.08,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Right here, right now... \NI'm going to surpass my limits!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.55,0:17:54.41,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,This is everything...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.74,0:17:58.81,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,that I've got right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.67,0:18:07.35,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,The reason I've been able to fight \Nup until now is all thanks to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.35,0:18:10.01,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,So seriously, thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.57,0:18:14.95,main,Liebe,0000,0000,0000,,Did you seriously just say that to \Nthe guy who stole your right arm?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.95,0:18:16.96,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that was the deal!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.96,0:18:18.41,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I've got no complaints!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.41,0:18:22.26,main,Liebe,0000,0000,0000,,You really are so unbelievably stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.26,0:18:26.08,main,Liebe,0000,0000,0000,,And that's exactly why I'm about to kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.44,0:18:29.08,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I can't let you do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.36,0:18:32.50,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,And, hey! I just remembered \Nour first conversation!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.51,0:18:37.26,flashback,Devil,0000,0000,0000,,A little dwarf like you \Nhas no chance of winning.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.61,0:18:41.00,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,But you're short, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.00,0:18:43.29,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,No fair acting all giant!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.29,0:18:45.68,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to get my butt \Nkicked by anyone like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.09,0:18:51.77,main,Liebe,0000,0000,0000,,You moron. I guess you still don't \Nunderstand the situation you're in.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.78,0:18:59.65,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Demon-Slayer!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.90,0:19:05.93,main,Liebe,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way you're winning this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.13,0:19:13.38,main,Liebe,0000,0000,0000,,You just walked right into my turf.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.73,0:19:15.61,main,Liebe,0000,0000,0000,,This time, it won't just be your right arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.61,0:19:18.38,main,Liebe,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be taking all of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.02,0:19:22.65,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it, you jerk! I don't \Nintend to fight you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.65,0:19:23.39,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna talk—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.39,0:19:24.63,main,Nacht,0000,0000,0000,,Fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.09,0:19:28.93,main,Nacht,0000,0000,0000,,You came here to become stronger, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.45,0:19:32.11,main,Nacht,0000,0000,0000,,Then defeat him, whatever it takes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.11,0:19:35.93,main,Nacht,0000,0000,0000,,If you lose... the devil \Nwill take over your body,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.93,0:19:37.98,main,Nacht,0000,0000,0000,,and you'll become a grotesque monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.40,0:19:43.82,main,Nacht,0000,0000,0000,,All the skulls you see in the altar are \Nthose who failed the devil-binding ritual.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.34,0:19:47.66,main,Nacht,0000,0000,0000,,If you fail, I'll dispose of you and \Nadd your skull to the collection.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.46,0:19:53.50,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't this... forbidden magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.00,0:19:59.67,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, is the devil-binding ritual \Nsomething we shouldn't be doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.67,0:20:01.26,main,Nacht,0000,0000,0000,,We only have two days.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.32,0:20:05.39,main,Nacht,0000,0000,0000,,Did you actually think you'd become \Nstronger using decent methods?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.49,0:20:10.58,main,Nacht,0000,0000,0000,,This is the world you stepped \Ninto because you have
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.58,0:20:13.10,main,Nacht,0000,0000,0000,,no magic and wanted to become stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.83,0:20:22.21,main,Nacht,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.21,0:20:24.11,main,Nacht,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, he's going to kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.11,0:20:26.12,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.54,0:20:30.41,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,He's not actually trying to kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.41,0:20:31.62,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I can tell from his ki.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.64,0:20:37.46,main,Nacht,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about? \NThe one in front of you is a devil.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.46,0:20:39.88,main,Nacht,0000,0000,0000,,Devils don't have any principles.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.34,0:20:46.64,main,Liebe,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! Every single devil \Nout there is a piece of shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.01,0:20:50.27,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,This guy isn't like the \Ndevil I fought before.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.52,0:20:53.52,main,Liebe,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna steal your body and—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.52,0:20:54.98,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Just because you're a devil...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.67,0:20:59.23,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,doesn't automatically make you a bad guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.92,0:21:05.91,main,Liebe,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.05,0:21:09.18,main,Licita and Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.44,0:21:15.01,flashback,Licita,0000,0000,0000,,You're not a bad guy!
