Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.89,0:22:49.94,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Petit Clover!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.05,0:22:54.06,sign_33188_278_The_Mystery_of_t,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(520,1)}Vice Captain
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.24,0:22:52.35,main,Nacht,0000,0000,0000,,Vice Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.72,0:22:55.93,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.93,0:22:59.00,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,The Black Bulls don't have a vice captain, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.49,0:23:02.90,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you know how Captain Yami is.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.90,0:23:05.19,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,It's gotta be rough being his vice captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.74,0:23:09.32,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,They'd need to be able to \Nkeep up with his drinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.82,0:23:14.45,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,They'd also need to be tolerant enough to \Ndeal with any of his ridiculous requests.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.05,0:23:19.62,main,Grey,0000,0000,0000,,Th-They'd need to be powerful enough \Nto keep up with his heroics!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.21,0:23:25.01,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,And they need enough patience \Nto deal with his long shits.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.46,0:23:28.00,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Man, that's rough.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.54,0:23:33.87,main,Nacht,0000,0000,0000,,The Black Bulls...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.54,0:23:35.61,main,Nacht,0000,0000,0000,,I hate them.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.67,0:23:42.35,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,In this world where magic is everything,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.35,0:23:45.31,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,there was one boy who couldn't use magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.31,0:23:49.74,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,He never gave up on the future, \Nno matter what challenges he faced.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.74,0:23:53.68,italics,Some,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on {\i1}Black Clover{\i0}, Page 170:\N "The Faraway Future."
